they have the right to be happy.

545
00:40:44,088 --> 00:40:47,758
That means we come to school to be happy.

546
00:40:49,969 --> 00:40:51,011
So,

547
00:40:51,554 --> 00:40:53,639
any bastard who gets in the way of that…

548
00:41:01,313 --> 00:41:02,648
no matter who they are…

549
00:41:04,525 --> 00:41:07,152
will be taught a lesson.

550
00:41:22,001 --> 00:41:23,502
I'm sorry.

551
00:41:24,211 --> 00:41:25,296
Please spare me.

552
00:41:25,379 --> 00:41:26,839
