553
00:41:26,922 --> 00:41:27,965
Please.

554
00:41:28,841 --> 00:41:30,217
Please give me another chance.

555
00:41:31,385 --> 00:41:33,971
Chances aren't something you're given.

556
00:41:35,180 --> 00:41:37,558
They come to those who want them.

557
00:41:41,937 --> 00:41:45,816
<i>I wanted to give you a chance.</i>

558
00:41:47,693 --> 00:41:49,236
<i>But Gyu-cheol,</i>

559
00:41:50,613 --> 00:41:52,114
<i>the thing is,</i>

560
00:41:53,616 --> 00:41:55,159
<i>chances aren't given to you.</i>

561
00:41:58,370 --> 00:42:00,914
Chances only come to those who want them.

562
00:42:05,919 --> 00:42:07,004
<i>Wow.</i>

563
