Just kill me instead.

571
00:42:40,329 --> 00:42:42,623
Go on. Kill me.

572
00:42:43,791 --> 00:42:45,167
I said kill me.

573
00:43:18,325 --> 00:43:21,078
Gyu-cheol, you shouldn't do this.

574
00:43:21,954 --> 00:43:23,205
It's okay.

575
