Let's start over.

576
00:43:46,603 --> 00:43:50,149
This is the last chance
Ms. Choi is giving you.

577
00:44:05,205 --> 00:44:07,750
Fuck!

578
00:44:09,710 --> 00:44:12,254
Who do you think you all are?

579
00:44:13,088 --> 00:44:15,257
You think you're Jesus?

580
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:17,134
A damn Buddha, or what?

581
00:44:17,217 --> 00:44:20,512
Fuck!

582
