Shall I get you a stapler?

585
00:46:08,203 --> 00:46:09,288
Oh man.

586
00:46:10,163 --> 00:46:11,665
Don't make me laugh.

587
00:46:28,682 --> 00:46:29,975
For fuck's sake!

588
00:46:30,058 --> 00:46:31,143
I'm going! Damn it.

589
00:46:32,311 --> 00:46:34,229
-You'll be okay.
-Thank you.

590
00:46:36,023 --> 00:46:38,442
-Let go of me.
-Let go, damn it.

591
00:46:39,109 --> 00:46:40,319
Fucking hell.

592
00:46:40,402 --> 00:46:41,820
I'm going, man!

593
00:46:49,328 --> 00:46:50,412
You

594
00:46:51,121 --> 00:46:52,748
are being charged

595
00:46:53,665 --> 00:46:55,208
with violations of the ERPB Act,

596
00:46:56,335 --> 00:46:57,669
