-The ERPB will also follow protocol.
-Yes, sir.

605
00:47:47,386 --> 00:47:48,929
Hey, what happened to you?

606
00:47:51,014 --> 00:47:51,848
Were you stabbed?

607
00:47:51,932 --> 00:47:53,600
-Well, yeah. I'm fine.
-Are you okay?

608
00:47:53,684 --> 00:47:55,227
-That bastard!
-Hey, stop him!

609
00:47:56,353 --> 00:47:57,354
Hey, you punk!

610
00:47:57,437 --> 00:47:59,356
-That's my son-in-law, you punk!
-Stop.

611
00:47:59,439 --> 00:48:02,359
Get out here! You punk, come here!

612
00:48:02,442 --> 00:48:04,403
-Come here!
-Go.

613
00:48:04,486 --> 00:48:05,904
-Minister, please.
-Please go!

614
00:48:05,988 --> 00:48:06,905
Come here, bastard!

615
00:48:06,989 --> 00:48:09,449
-Hold on, Minister.
-Come back! Hey!

616
00:48:10,117 --> 00:48:11,618
-Hey!
-Minister, wait.

617
00:48:11,702 --> 00:48:13,662
-Are you okay?
-Are you all right?

618
00:48:13,745 --> 00:48:15,080
MINISTRY OF EDUCATION

619
00:48:15,163 --> 00:48:16,206
<i>Fellow citizens,</i>

620
00:48:16,707 --> 00:48:19,209
do you know the definition of education?

621
00:48:20,043 --> 00:48:23,630
"The teaching of knowledge and skills
and the cultivation of character."

622
00:48:24,131 --> 00:48:26,174
This is what education is.

623
00:48:26,925 --> 00:48:29,970
Yes, good universities and good jobs
are important.

624
00:48:30,053 --> 00:48:31,596
But what's more important

625
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:35,976
is nurturing a person's dignity
and moral integrity.

626
00:48:36,059 --> 00:48:40,147
This is putting the true meaning
of education into practice.

627
00:48:41,606 --> 00:48:46,361
<i>However, the current education system</i>
<i>of our country has strayed too far</i>

628
00:48:46,445 --> 00:48:48,572
<i>from this purpose and is deeply broken.</i>

629
00:48:50,073 --> 00:48:52,993
<i>Nonetheless, in the midst of this reality,</i>

630
00:48:53,952 --> 00:48:57,873
<i>most teachers in this country</i>
<i>continue to fulfill their calling,</i>

631
00:48:57,956 --> 00:49:01,793
<i>teaching children and trying to guide them</i>
<i>toward the right path.</i>

632
00:49:10,886 --> 00:49:13,555
How long must we continue to see

633
00:49:14,389 --> 00:49:15,599
students and teachers

634
00:49:16,349 --> 00:49:19,394
never making it back home

635
00:49:20,771 --> 00:49:22,439
from school?

636
00:49:24,941 --> 00:49:28,487
The ERPB will uphold
the value of education

637
00:49:29,279 --> 00:49:30,781
and protect victims…

638
00:49:32,699 --> 00:49:35,952
until schools are no longer places
of fear and anxiety

639
00:49:36,703 --> 00:49:38,371
and become truly safe.

640
00:49:38,455 --> 00:49:41,833
We will continue to exist
until our education system is restored…

641
00:49:44,211 --> 00:49:45,629
to its intended state.

642
00:49:56,640 --> 00:50:01,394
I MISS YOUR SMILE SO MUCH

