I'm Deputy Director Bong Geun-dae
from the ERPB.

735
00:54:22,197 --> 00:54:23,490
From this moment on,

736
00:54:24,366 --> 00:54:25,825
the ERPB

737
00:54:27,410 --> 00:54:28,703
will teach you a lesson.

738
00:54:31,414 --> 00:54:32,248
Get up.

739
00:54:32,957 --> 00:54:33,833
I said get up.

740
00:54:33,917 --> 00:54:35,502
You too. Step back.

741
00:54:36,711 --> 00:54:37,837
Get up.

742
00:54:37,921 --> 00:54:39,381
I said get up.

743
