745
00:54:52,227 --> 00:54:53,978
No, I said "get off" me.

746
00:54:54,062 --> 00:54:55,230
You said to get up.

747
00:54:55,313 --> 00:54:57,315
-No, I said, "Get off."
-Oh man.

748
00:54:57,399 --> 00:54:59,401
-You said to get up.
-No, I said, "Get off."

749
00:54:59,484 --> 00:55:02,404
-I said…
-Take your hands off him. Now!

750
00:55:03,071 --> 00:55:03,905
Who's that?

751
00:55:05,657 --> 00:55:06,741
Get up.

752
00:55:08,243 --> 00:55:09,411
Get up!

753
