778
00:57:07,779 --> 00:57:09,197
-Let's get you up.
-Are you okay?

779
00:57:11,783 --> 00:57:12,784
Mark my words.

780
00:57:13,284 --> 00:57:16,621
I'll be back no matter what.
The first thing I'll do is take you down.

781
00:57:21,543 --> 00:57:24,045
When Cho Gyu-cheol gave you the recording,

782
00:57:25,004 --> 00:57:26,130
you knew what happened.

783
00:57:27,090 --> 00:57:28,883
You should've stopped then.

784
00:57:29,676 --> 00:57:33,721
It's adults like you
who turn young students into monsters.

785
00:57:34,222 --> 00:57:37,225
If you can't be a good adult,
at least don't be a bad one.

786
00:57:38,226 --> 00:57:40,812
And what about you? Are you a good adult?

787
00:57:40,895 --> 00:57:43,815
You think I won't find anything on you?
Damn…

788
00:57:57,704 --> 00:57:58,538
I guess

789
00:58:00,123 --> 00:58:03,293
I'm not a good adult either.

790
00:59:28,878 --> 00:59:31,839
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim

